    public static String generateCamelCase(String label){

        if(label == null || label.isEmpty())
            return label;

        label = label.trim();
        String[] words = label.split("\\W+");

        sb.append(Character.toUpperCase(words[0].charAt(0)));

        if(words[0].length() > 1) {
            sb.append(words[0].substring(1).toLowerCase());
        }
